---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ProofLabs Launch Checklist - Admin"
  description="Step-by-step instructions for launching ProofLabs and getting indexed by Google"
>
  <div style="max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;">
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fed7aa 100%); border: 2px solid var(--color-accent); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🚀</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
        ProofLabs Launch Checklist
      </h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0;">
        Everything you need to launch and grow ProofLabs
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Before Launch -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-accent); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        Before Launch (Do These Now)
      </h2>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          ✅ Google Search Console
        </h3>
        <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Go to <a href="https://search.google.com/search-console" target="_blank" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Google Search Console</a></li>
          <li>Sign in with your Google account</li>
          <li>Click "Add Property" → enter <code>https://prooflabs.net</code></li>
          <li>Choose verification method:
            <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
              <li><strong>Option A (Recommended):</strong> DNS verification — Add a TXT record to your Cloudflare DNS settings</li>
              <li><strong>Option B:</strong> HTML file — Download the file, replace <code>public/google-verification.html</code>, push to main</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>Once verified, go to "Sitemaps" in the left sidebar</li>
          <li>Enter <code>sitemap-index.xml</code> and click "Submit"</li>
          <li>Google will start crawling within hours to days</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          ✅ Bing Webmaster Tools
        </h3>
        <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Go to <a href="https://www.bing.com/webmasters" target="_blank" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Bing Webmaster Tools</a></li>
          <li>Sign in and add <code>https://prooflabs.net</code></li>
          <li>Import directly from Google Search Console (easiest)</li>
          <li>Submit sitemap: <code>https://prooflabs.net/sitemap-index.xml</code></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          ✅ Google Analytics 4
        </h3>
        <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Go to <a href="https://analytics.google.com" target="_blank" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Google Analytics</a></li>
          <li>Create a new GA4 property for prooflabs.net</li>
          <li>Get the measurement ID (starts with <code>G-</code>)</li>
          <li>Add tracking snippet to <code>src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro</code> in the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          ✅ Cloudflare Settings
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Verify HTTPS is enforced (auto with Cloudflare Pages)</li>
          <li>Enable "Always Use HTTPS" in SSL/TLS settings</li>
          <li>Check www redirect (www.prooflabs.net → prooflabs.net)</li>
          <li>Enable "Auto Minify" for HTML/CSS/JS (optional)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- First Week -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-secondary); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        First Week After Launch
      </h2>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Request Indexing for Priority Pages
        </h3>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          In Search Console, use URL Inspection to request indexing (~10 per day max):
        </p>
        <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/strategies/secret-sauce</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/strategies/how-to-pay-rent-with-credit-card</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/credit-cards/best-credit-card-for-rent</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/strategies/credit-card-stacking</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/find-cards</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/about</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/articles/best-credit-card-for-groceries</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/articles/best-credit-card-for-gas</li>
          <li>https://prooflabs.net/articles/best-credit-card-for-online-shopping</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Set Up Rank Tracking
        </h3>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Track these keywords in Search Console Performance or a rank tracker:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem; columns: 2; column-gap: 2rem;">
          <li>pay rent with credit card</li>
          <li>best credit card for rent</li>
          <li>credit card stacking</li>
          <li>best credit card for groceries 2026</li>
          <li>best credit card for gas 2026</li>
          <li>Rakuten cashback guide</li>
          <li>BILT credit card review</li>
          <li>best 3 card combo</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Social Profiles (E-E-A-T Signals)
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Create X/Twitter account for ProofLabs</li>
          <li>Create LinkedIn profile or page</li>
          <li>Add social URLs to Organization schema in SEO.astro</li>
          <li>Consider Reddit presence in r/creditcards, r/churning, r/personalfinance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Backlink Starter Actions
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Submit to Product Hunt (the Card Stack Builder)</li>
          <li>Submit to IndieHackers (share the build story)</li>
          <li>Share on Hacker News ("Show HN")</li>
          <li>Write 2-3 helpful Reddit comments with natural links</li>
          <li>Sign up for Connectively (formerly HARO) for journalist queries</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- First Month -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text); border-bottom: 3px solid #10b981; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        First Month After Launch
      </h2>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Content Publishing
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Publish 2-3 articles per week from /admin/content-calendar</li>
          <li>Priority: Week 3-4 articles (dining, Costco, no-annual-fee)</li>
          <li>Convert coming-soon pages to real content</li>
          <li>Each new article = sitemap auto-updates</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Email Platform Connection
        </h3>
        <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Choose: Beehiiv (free up to 2,500) or ConvertKit</li>
          <li>Set up account and create list/audience</li>
          <li>Update all EmailCapture components to real API</li>
          <li>Create the Google Sheets spreadsheet lead magnet</li>
          <li>Set up 5-email welcome sequence</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Affiliate Program Applications
        </h3>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>Credit card programs:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          <li>American Express affiliate program</li>
          <li>Chase affiliate program</li>
          <li>Citi, Discover, Capital One, Bank of America</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 1rem 0;"><strong>Affiliate networks:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          <li>Commission Junction (CJ)</li>
          <li>FlexOffers</li>
          <li>Impact.com</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 1rem 0;"><strong>Platform referrals:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          <li>Robinhood, SoFi, Wealthfront, Webull</li>
          <li>Coinbase affiliate program</li>
          <li>Rakuten referral program</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--color-success); margin-top: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600;">
          → Once approved, replace all <code>&lt;!-- TODO: affiliate link --&gt;</code> with tracked links
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Mascot Illustrations
        </h3>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Use <code>/admin/mascot-brief</code> to commission illustrations:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Fiverr: search "mascot character illustration" ($100-300 for 15 poses)</li>
          <li>Or generate with Midjourney/DALL-E using brief prompts</li>
          <li>Save to <code>/public/mascot/</code> as SVG + PNG</li>
          <li>Replace all 🦔 emoji placeholders with real illustrations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ongoing -->
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text); border-bottom: 3px solid #6366f1; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        Ongoing (Month 2+)
      </h2>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Content Machine
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>2-3 articles/week from content calendar</li>
          <li>Convert coming-soon pages in priority order</li>
          <li>Update existing articles when card terms change</li>
          <li>Add "Last updated" dates when refreshing content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text);">
          Monitor & Optimize
        </h3>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
          <li>Check Search Console weekly — what queries are you ranking for?</li>
          <li>Which pages get the most traffic? Double down on those topics</li>
          <li>High impressions but low clicks? Optimize titles/descriptions</li>
          <li>Monitor affiliate conversion rates — which cards actually convert?</li>
          <li>A/B test CTA button copy on high-traffic pages</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fed7aa 100%); border: 2px solid var(--color-accent); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem; margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🎉</div>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0;">
        You're ready to launch ProofLabs!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
